    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_3_2631-2668",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2631-2668",
      "markText": "克明俊德，以亲九族。九族既睦，平章百姓。百姓昭明，协和万邦，黎民於变时雍。",
      "totalCount": 390,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2631&rangeEnd=2668",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2631&rangeEnd=2668"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_3_597-628",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "597-628",
      "markText": "昔在帝尧，聪明文思，光宅天下。将逊于位，让于虞舜，作《尧典》。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=597&rangeEnd=628",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=597&rangeEnd=628"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_3_1704-1737",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1704-1737",
      "markText": "曰若稽古，帝尧曰放勋，钦明文思安安，允恭克让。光被四表，格于上下。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1704&rangeEnd=1737",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1704&rangeEnd=1737"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_6_745-760",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "745-760",
      "markText": "禹敷土，随山刊木，奠高山大川。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=745&rangeEnd=760",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=745&rangeEnd=760"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_3_994-1021",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "994-1021",
      "markText": "虞舜侧微，尧闻之聪明。将使嗣位，历试诸难，作《舜典》。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=994&rangeEnd=1021",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=994&rangeEnd=1021"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_3_3063-3085",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3063-3085",
      "markText": "乃命羲和，钦若昊天，历象日月星辰，敬授民时。",
      "totalCount": 143,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3063&rangeEnd=3085",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3063&rangeEnd=3085"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_3_11081-11176",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "11081-11176",
      "markText": "帝曰：“咨，四岳，汤汤洪水方割，荡荡怀山襄陵，浩浩滔天。下民共咨，有能俾乂。”佥曰：“於，鲧哉。”帝曰：“吁，咈哉，方命圮族。”岳曰：“异哉，试可乃已。”帝曰：“往，钦哉。”九载，绩用弗成。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=11081&rangeEnd=11176",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=11081&rangeEnd=11176"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_3_13253-13288",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "13253-13288",
      "markText": "帝曰：“格，汝舜。询事考言，乃言可绩，三载。汝陟帝位。”舜让于德弗嗣。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=13253&rangeEnd=13288",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=13253&rangeEnd=13288"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_5_4906-4925",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4906-4925",
      "markText": "天聪明，自我民聪明。天明畏，自我民明威",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4906&rangeEnd=4925",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4906&rangeEnd=4925"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_35_1346-1364",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "1346-1364",
      "markText": "“称尔戈，比尔干，立尔矛，予其誓。”",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=1346&rangeEnd=1364",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=1346&rangeEnd=1364"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_35_465-492",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "465-492",
      "markText": "武王戎车三百两，虎贲三百人，与受战于牧野，作《牧誓》。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=465&rangeEnd=492",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=465&rangeEnd=492"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_3_18073-18108",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "18073-18108",
      "markText": "流共工于幽州，放驩兜于崇山，窜三苗于三危，殛鲧于羽山，四罪而天下咸服。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=18073&rangeEnd=18108",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=18073&rangeEnd=18108"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_5_2022-2101",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2022-2101",
      "markText": "皋陶曰：“都，在知人，在安民。”禹曰：“吁，咸若时，惟帝其难之。知人则哲，能官人。安民则惠，黎民怀之。能哲而惠，何忧乎驩兜，何迁乎有苗，何畏乎巧言令色孔壬？”",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2022&rangeEnd=2101",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2022&rangeEnd=2101"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_6_526-541",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "526-541",
      "markText": "禹别九州，随山浚川，任土作贡。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=526&rangeEnd=541",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=526&rangeEnd=541"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_37_2862-2928",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "2862-2928",
      "markText": "“二，五事。一曰貌，二曰言，三曰视，四曰听，五曰思。貌曰恭，言曰从，视曰明，听曰聪，思曰睿。恭作肃，从作乂，明作晢，聪作谋，睿作圣。",
      "totalCount": 77,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=2862&rangeEnd=2928",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=2862&rangeEnd=2928"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793593_2_700-742",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "700-742",
      "markText": "西汉初伏生所藏壁中《尚书》尚存二十八篇，以西汉当时通行文字隶书抄写，故称《今文尚书》",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793593&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=700&rangeEnd=742",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/abc323c071c69d39abca9a1?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=700&rangeEnd=742"
